{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":6,"day":3}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"无题","authors":["王建华"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载，在林彪、“四人帮”迫害下，少奇同志含冤逝世，火化时，证书职业栏里竟填的是“无业”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“无业”，“无业”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家主席竟“无业”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么滑稽的插曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么荒唐的岁月！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国正值一日千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩劫却闯入应该收获的季节；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理失去生存的空间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谬误却在肆行暴虐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有业无业，历史记得——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋起安源，曙光初射；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜入平津，狂飚骤烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为将白区变苏区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几度衔命赴虎穴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运筹江淮大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐镇太行山侧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一席《论党》分正邪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一册《修养》助大业……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有业无业，这历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好在是由人民书写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣看乌云散处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民为他恢复了本色："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出生入死，革命为业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功高如山，千秋不灭！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}